<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200924/9a5c64e87bf54848b82d0991f0aaf30c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作3、负重深蹲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200924/25df168073e2453183f66d6a6817bf0a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作4、哑铃侧平举</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200924/b52cfc7e849b42d0bd3c14a28dfeec7f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
